{
  "stem": "304.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No matter how religious you were, there was still somebody who was more or less.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only him, the whole family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we felt so degraded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they knew that the beard is for religious reasons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is why they did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or just showing you cannot observe what you want, you cannot do what you want.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will tell you what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And another incident was with my uncle who had the bar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Peasants used come in to drink and they were very often drunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they paid, he gave them change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during the Hungarians, one man did it once, and they learned from it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he will give, let's say $5 and my uncle wants to give him back change from $5.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, oh no, I gave you $20.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, no, I-- you gave me $5.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then he will run out on the street, find a policeman, bring him back to the store, and say, I gave him $5-- $20 and he doesn't want to give me back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the policeman forced my uncle to give him change from $20.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then put-- beat him up and put him to jail for a-- for a few days without asking any questions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was an everyday occurrence in different forms and ways.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, I'm just bringing this as an example how we suffered from antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course in the school, I felt it also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Day in and day out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] From students and from the teachers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember one teacher very, very kindly, an older lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we were hassled around or beaten up by other students because we are Jewish, we came to her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We told her.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
